text: Elmore County is a county in the U.S. state of Idaho. As of the 2020 census, 28,666 people lived there. The county seat and largest city is Mountain Home. == Communities == === Cities === * Glenns Ferry * Mountain Home === Census- designated places === * Hammett * Mountain Home Air Force Base === Unincorporated communities === * Atlanta * Dixie * Featherville * King Hill * Pine * Tipanuk === Ghost town === * Rocky Bar == References == Category:1880s establishments in Idaho Territory Category:1889 establishments in the United States Category:Idaho counties
